    <item>
      <title>特朗普前首席财务官艾伦·韦塞尔伯格被判处五个月监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ex-trump-cfo-weisselberg-is-sentenced-to-five-months-in-jail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)房地产公司的长期首席财务官艾伦·韦塞尔伯格(Allen Weisselberg)因在纽约针对这位前总统的民事欺诈案中宣誓就职而被判处五个月监禁，这是他第二次入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ex-trump-cfo-weisselberg-is-sentenced-to-five-months-in-jail</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:41:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在 1 万亿美元的 AI 反弹之后，Meta 交易以折扣价进行七巨头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/meta-trades-at-a-discount-to-magnificent-seven-after-1-trillion-ai-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2022 年最黑暗的日子以来，Meta Platforms Inc. 在人工智能推动下破纪录的上涨使市值增加了 1 万亿美元，但从某些角度来看，它的交易价格仍然存在折扣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/meta-trades-at-a-discount-to-magnificent-seven-after-1-trillion-ai-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:41:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管科技进步，股票对冲基金未能超越基准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/equity-hedge-funds-fail-to-beat-benchmarks-despite-tech-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[得益于一些雄心勃勃的科技公司，选股对冲基金第一季度的涨幅超过任何其他主要策略——但它仍然不足以击败市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/equity-hedge-funds-fail-to-beat-benchmarks-despite-tech-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国赤字超出预期，给马克龙带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/french-deficit-to-widen-even-more-raising-pressure-on-macron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府表示，随着埃马纽埃尔·马克龙削减开支的压力加大，其赤字将比预期更大——或者寻找新的国家收入来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/french-deficit-to-widen-even-more-raising-pressure-on-macron</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:54:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
