    <item>
      <title>达美航空预计第二季度利润和销售额超出华尔街预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/delta-forecasts-2q-profit-sales-to-beat-expectations-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于夏季旅游旺季之前商务旅行的增加和休闲需求的稳定，达美航空预计第二季度利润和收入将超过华尔街的预测。彭博资讯 (Bloomberg Intelligence) 的乔治·弗格森 (George Ferguson) 在彭博电视台 (Bloomberg Television) 上有更多报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/delta-forecasts-2q-profit-sales-to-beat-expectations-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:58:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯石油价格再次远高于七国集团的价格上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/russian-oil-is-once-again-trading-far-above-the-g-7-s-price-cap-everywhere</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯石油的交易量远远超过了七国集团的价格上限，这本应剥夺莫斯科在乌克兰战争中的收入，这表明俄罗斯严重违反了该措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/russian-oil-is-once-again-trading-far-above-the-g-7-s-price-cap-everywhere</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:36:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着降息的消退，盈利是股市走强的最后支柱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/wall-street-sees-earnings-propelling-defiant-stock-rally-onward</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三上午公布的通胀数据超出预期，几乎消除了近期降息的可能性。这使得盈利成为支撑去年开始的股市反弹的最后一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/wall-street-sees-earnings-propelling-defiant-stock-rally-onward</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着消费者物价指数 (CPI) 关上美联储 6 月转向的大门，股市下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份高于预期的通胀报告表明美联储今年不会急于降息后，华尔街交易员导致股票和债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:14:02 GMT</pubDate>
